Fenox smiles at Vlad. "You're welcome. Here, follow me."

She walks down the hall toward the residential areas, motioning for 
Vlad to follow.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Carnage Blood" <Carnage@d...> wrote:
> ** Vlad could hear things going on inside of the Iorn Fist, which 
reminded him of a battle he was in when he had first arrived here on 
this strange world. Shesta whinned and paced a bit at his heels, 
perhaps sensing something he could not. All natural animals seemed 
that way.
> He cleared his throat and nodded once Fenox had told him that he 
was accepted to stay and would show him to his quarters for the time 
which he would be there. Which seemed logical.** " Um...thanks." ** 
Shesta tilts her head while looking towards Fenox.**
